---
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use bun for package management
- Always use shadcn components and install via the script: `bunx shadcn@latest add <component>`
- Use Image from next/image for all images.
- Use Link from next/link for app links and <a> for external links.
- Break down complex components into smaller components.
- Use kebab-case naming convention for file names.
- Use Lucide React for icons.
- Use cn from @/lib/utils for all class name merging.
- Never create markdown files (.md) after you are done explaining your changes. Never!
- Never cast to any type. Always use correct types.
- Write db mutations and queries in app/api as api routes.
- Use useEffects only if you absolutely need to. Don't implement otherwise.
- Calling setState synchronously within an effect can trigger cascading renders. Dont call setState in useEffects.
- use z.email() instead of z.string().email()
